OL,3,C'No official record' to show Epstein
OL,4,Cstayed at Hillsborough Castle
OL,6,FNo official records have been found
OL,7,Fwhich show the convicted paedophile
OL,8,FJeffrey Epstein stayed at or visited
OL,9,FHillsborough Castle.
OL,11,FFiles released by the United States
OL,12,FDepartment of Justice have linked Lord
OL,13,FMandelson and the disgraced financier.
OL,15,FHowever, after a search of government
OL,16,Frecords there has been no information
OL,17,Ffound to suggest that Mandelson had
OL,18,Fany official contact with Epstein
OL,19,Fduring the Labour peer's time as
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland secretary.
