OL,3,C'No official record' to show Epstein
OL,4,Cstayed at Hillsborough Castle
OL,6,FUUP Leader Jon Burrows had asked the
OL,7,FSecretary of State Hilary Benn to
OL,8,Fconfirm if there were any government
OL,9,Frecords about such meetings.
OL,11,FMr Benn has now written to Mr Burrows
OL,12,Fconfirming no records were found.
OL,14,FLord Mandelson served as Secretary of
OL,15,FState for Northern Ireland between
OL,16,FOctober 1999 and January 2001.
OL,18,FHe was arrested on Monday on suspicion
OL,19,Fof misconduct in public office and
OL,20,Flater released on bail in the early
OL,21,Fhours of Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
